title: Andy Carroll is a loser and Lou can do better - but she's absolutely obsessed with him: Lou Teasdale's friends tell KATIE HIND why she's really back with the footballer - and why they fear she will take this dramatic next step

description: As she kissed Marshall good night and crept out of his bedroom, she made her way into her own room. There, she sat on her bed and chopped up a line of cocaine with her bank card.
title: When I found out I was pregnant, the first thing I did was phone my dealer and go on a cocaine binge for several days. My nightly habit continued after giving birth... and I've discovered there are many mothers like me

description: Emily Atack plays her to perfection: rude, smug, false and, underneath the facade, deeply unhappy.
title: CHRISTOPHER STEVENS reviews The Rumour: Emily Atack's spiteful school mum ought to have been in Motherland
